std::string sbwSignature::consumeName (  const char *&    signature )  [static]
 

parse a given string extracting the front substring.

The front substring is terminated by any of the following characters: {}[](), as well as whitespace and the null terminator. Any initial whitespace is ignored/skipped.

Parameters:
signature  string to be parsed, this string pointer value is changed to point beyond the extracted substring
Returns:
the extracted substring (doesn't include any leading whitespace)
